00:10:19.068 --> 00:10:24.268
<i>For two blind loves</i>

139
00:10:35.540 --> 00:10:38.169
<i>Two blind loves</i>

140
00:10:38.269 --> 00:10:41.049
<i>Two blind loves</i>

141
00:10:41.149 --> 00:10:44.525
<i>Do we know what we're doing?</i>

142
