<i>Two blind loves</i>

143
00:10:47.429 --> 00:10:50.166
<i>Don't know from appetite</i>

144
00:10:50.266 --> 00:10:53.129
<i>Don't know fish from steak</i>

145
00:10:53.229 --> 00:10:56.328
<i>Don't know if it's a doughnut</i>

146
00:10:56.428 --> 00:10:59.129
<i>Or a wedding cake</i>

147
00:10:59.229 --> 00:11:04.169
<i>I only know the sun started to shine</i>

148
